cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with learning robust visual representation and improving object categorization and localization performance. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a semi-supervised learning approach. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of visual models. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with large sets of unlabeled images. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper proposes a distributed approximate nearest neighbor algorithm for retrieval of visual self-regularizers.
